BinaryBuddies

Binary Buddies Memory Management System

Justin Patriquin - B00549827 -- Logan Pitman - B00533117

Acknowledgements

buddytree.c and buddytree.h are highly modified versions of a binary search tree taken from the online book Learn C the Hard Way.

Test Cases

1. Test to make sure the the function returns actual addresses.
2. Test to make sure the user memory references can't be used after freeing them with release_memory.
3. Test to make sure the leafs nodes are created when a user asks for memory.
4. Test to make sure the leaf node is removed when a user release memory using release_memory.
5. Test to make sure actually data can be put into the address space.
